data.description: Check out the potential that this 2 bedroom, with 1 non conforming bedroom/study with access to back door, mudroom, over-sized pantry, kitchen has a vintage flare with functioning built-in ironing board, furnace & duct work is less than 10 years old, water heater less than 5 years old, new sewer line put in 2017, new vinyl windows & blinds throughout home, basement is unfinished but has potential for additional living space, large backyard with alley access for plenty of off street parking, walking distance to Fountain International Magnet School, Public transportation routs, minutes to downtown, Belmont shopping & restaurants  and easy I-25 access, has!
